1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,360
The three minor demons turned back at
once. Blood from the dead cat still clung
to the scaled one's mouth.

2
00:00:04,960 --> 00:00:07,672
Where did this discarded consort crawl out
from, talking so big?

3
00:00:08,072 --> 00:00:11,039
Return the rent? Give us your flesh for a
midnight snack first!

4
00:00:11,439 --> 00:00:17,556
I did not answer. I watched. The three
demons spread into a loose triangle; the
old locust stood behind them, and my only
retreat was the low wall at my side.

5
00:00:17,956 --> 00:00:24,010
I could fight, but not for long. I only
had stealth; I could not borrow brute
strength. If I fought all three head-on, I
would not last ten breaths.

6
00:00:24,610 --> 00:00:25,869
Then I would not fight head-on.

7
00:00:26,269 --> 00:00:34,269
I lowered my eyes, and my figure faded
three shades into the tree shadow. The
split-mouth demon lunged first, fangs
wide, aiming for my throat.

8
00:00:34,669 --> 00:00:40,240
I did not retreat. I stepped in. Stealth
swallowed my footsteps; it missed, and its
whole neck stretched out.

9
00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:45,909
I slipped behind its neck, locked my
fingers around its throat, and used its
own momentum to drag it into the old
locust trunk.

10
00:00:46,309 --> 00:00:47,459
Ah!

11
00:00:47,859 --> 00:00:50,155
Thud. Two rows of jagged teeth shattered
loose.

12
00:00:50,855 --> 00:00:52,005
Refine.

13
00:00:52,405 --> 00:00:55,015
Demon body detected. Refine it?

14
00:00:55,415 --> 00:00:56,565
Yes.

15
00:00:56,965 --> 00:01:04,965
Black smoke surged from that torn mouth
and drilled through my fingers into my
blood. A vision exploded in my mind: it
could mimic human voices and speech.

16
00:01:05,365 --> 00:01:08,317
Demon-devouring extraction. Ability
available: Voice Capture, Imitation
Speech.

17
00:01:08,917 --> 00:01:12,670
Useless. Imitation was a hidden trick, a
deception. It would not help me establish
power now.

18
00:01:13,070 --> 00:01:19,186
But the other two were already charging.
The scaled one growled, while the
twig-finger demon flanked from behind, its
barbs flashing under the moon.

19
00:01:19,586 --> 00:01:26,094
There was only one thing I needed to stand
firm in this cold palace: the ability to
take a hit.

20
00:01:26,694 --> 00:01:31,963
The instant the scaled demon slammed
toward me, I did not dodge. I turned past
the barbs and pressed my hand onto its
spine.

21
00:01:32,363 --> 00:01:33,622
You are the one.

22
00:01:34,022 --> 00:01:37,641
Demon body detected. Scaled demon. Scale
armor, hard defense.

23
00:01:38,041 --> 00:01:39,191
Refine.

24
00:01:39,891 --> 00:01:45,342
This time, I was greedy. The split-mouth
demon's voice craft had not yet settled,
and the scaled demon's armor flooded in
after it.

25
00:01:45,742 --> 00:01:51,254
Two streams of demonic energy collided
inside me. My chest felt stuffed with a
red-hot coal, burning through blood and
bone.

26
00:01:51,854 --> 00:01:53,549
Same-origin rejection. Bloodline overload.

27
00:01:53,949 --> 00:01:55,099
Warning: greedy devouring backlash.

28
00:01:55,499 --> 00:02:03,499
My vision went red. Not blood. The entire
imperial city was veiled in red gauze,
turning into flesh I should swallow.
